=head1 DESCRIPTION

Identifies the source of the finding change event.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Identity => Str

The identity of the source that initiated the finding change event. For
example, the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of a partner that calls
BatchImportFindings or of a customer that calls BatchUpdateFindings.


=head2 Type => Str

Describes the type of finding change event, such as a call to
C<BatchImportFindings>
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/securityhub/1.0/APIReference/API_BatchImportFindings.html)
(by an integrated Amazon Web Services service or third party partner
integration) or C<BatchUpdateFindings>
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/securityhub/1.0/APIReference/API_BatchUpdateFindings.html)
(by a Security Hub customer).



